  (38,'verified','Welcome to Saatchi Online',NULL,'Dear {%profileName},\r\n\r\nWelcome to Saatchi Online. Your email address has been confirmed. Saatchi Online is unlike any other gallery in the world - we have an international audience of artists in over 190 countries. Having trouble finding a particular piece or are you not sure what you are looking for? Please contact us at support{%saatchionline}.com. We have thousands of beautiful art pieces and hundreds more uploaded weekly. Be sure to visit our online gallery often. Happy shopping!\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nSaatchi Online','Dear {%profileName},<br/><br/>Welcome to Saatchi Online. Your email address has been confirmed. Saatchi Online is unlike any other gallery in the world - we have an international audience of artists in over 190 countries. Having trouble finding a particular piece or are you not sure what you are looking for? Please contact us at support{%saatchionline}.com. We have thousands of beautiful art pieces and hundreds more uploaded weekly. Be sure to visit our online gallery often. Happy shopping!<br/><br/>Sincerely,<br/>Saatchi Online',40,0,1,'2013-05-24 09:17:05','noAuth'),
  (39,'win','You made it to the next round of Showdown.',NULL,'Dear {%profileName},\n\nYou advanced to the next round of Showdown and are 1 of {%numberRemaining} people remaining.\n\nBe sure to vote in the next round by clicking the link below.\n\n{%messageUrl}\n\nDid you know you can sell prints of this art on Saatchi Online? Click here http://www.saatchionline.com/guidelines to find out how.\n\nRegards,\nSaatchi Online','Dear {%profileName},<br/><br/>You advanced to the next round of Showdown and are 1 of {%numberRemaining} people remaining.<br/><br/>Be sure to vote in the next round by clicking the link below.<br/><br/><a href=\"{%messageUrl}\">{%messageUrl}</a><br/><br/>Did you know you can sell prints of this art on Saatchi Online? <a href=\"http://www.saatchionline.com/guidelines\">Click here</a> to find out how.<br/><br/>Regards,<br/>Saatchi Online',40,0,1,'2013-05-24 09:17:05','noAuth'),
