  (41,'artist_sales_notification','Saatchi Online has sold one of your original artworks','orders@saatchionline.com','Dear {%replacements.profileName},\r\n\r\nCongratulations! Saatchi Online has sold your artwork, {%replacements.artTitle} {%replacements.artUrl}. \r\n\r\nBefore we can help you ship your work, please verify that the artwork is still available:\r\n\r\nClick <a href=\"{%replacements.confirmLink}\">here</a> if you have the artwork available.\r\n\r\nClick <a href=\"{%replacements.disconfirmLink}\">here</a> if the artwork is no longer available.\r\n\r\nTo make shipment of your artwork easier for you, one of our Saatchi Online Customer Support team will be: \r\n\r\n- Scheduling a pick up. Please confirm your contact details below.\r\n- A pickup confirmation, shipping label, and any necessary documents (e.g. commercial invoice) will be emailed to you within 2 business days. \r\n\r\nDaytime Phone Number: {%replacements.phoneNumber}\r\n\r\nFor important guidance on how to package your artwork, click here http://www.saatchionline.com/packaging.\r\n\r\nYour sale proceeds will made available to you 7 days after successful delivery to the buyer in your Sales Dashboard under Account. Please make sure your tax forms have been filled out and sent to accounting@saatchionline.com to avoid any payout delays. \r\n\r\nThank you for selling your work on Saatchi Online.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nSaatchi Online','<p>Dear {%replacements.profileName},</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Congratulations! Saatchi Online has sold your artwork,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://{%replacements.artUrl}\">{%replacements.artTitle}</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before we can help you ship your work, please verify that the artwork is still available:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Click&nbsp;<a href=\"{%replacements.confirmlink}\">here</a>&nbsp;if you have the artwork available.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Click&nbsp;<a href=\"{%replacements.disconfirmlink}\">here</a>&nbsp;if the artwork is no longer available.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To make