  (42,'first_artist_artwork_availability_reminder','Your latest Saatchi Online Sale is in jeopardy','orders@saatchionline.com','Dear {%replacements.profileName},\r\n\r\nUnfortunately I have not heard back from you. Please act on this email immediately. \r\n\r\nWe have sold your artwork, <a href=\"http://{%replacements.artUrl}\">{%replacements.artTitle}</a>. \r\n\r\nBefore we can help you ship your work, please verify that the artwork is still available:\r\n\r\nClick {%replacements.confirmlink} if you have the artwork available, click {%replacements.disconfirmlink} if the artwork is no longer available.\r\n\r\nTo make shipment of your artwork easier for you, one of our Saatchi Online Customer Support team will be: \r\n\r\n- Scheduling a pick up. Please confirm your contact details below.\r\n- A pickup confirmation, shipping label, and any necessary documents (e.g. commercial invoice) will be emailed to you within 2 business days. \r\n\r\nDaytime Phone Number: {%replacements.phoneNumber}\r\n\r\nIt is urgent that you act on this message. If we don\'t hear back we will need to proceed to cancel this order. \r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nSaatchi Online','<p>Dear {%replacements.profileName},</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unfortunately I have not heard back from you. Please act on this email immediately.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have sold your artwork,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://{%replacements.artUrl}\">{%replacements.artTitle}</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before we can help you ship your work, please verify that the artwork is still available:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Click&nbsp;<a href=\"{%replacements.confirmlink}\">here</a>&nbsp;if you have the artwork available, click&nbsp;<a href=\"{%replacements.disconfirmlink}\">here</a>&nbsp;if the artwork is no longer available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To make shipment of your artwork easier for you, one of our Saatchi Online Customer Support team will be:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Scheduling a pick up. Please confirm your contact details below.<br />\r\n- A pickup confirmation, shipping label, a