  (45,'shipping_info_print','Your order item has been shipped - #{%increment_id}','orders@saatchionline.com','Dear {%replacements.profileName},\r\n\r\nSaatchi Online would like to let you know that we\'ve shipped your artwork.\r\n\r\nThe following item has been shipped to you:\r\n{%art_title}\r\n\r\nTrackingUrls:\r\n{%foreach data=tracking_urls item=item}\r\n{%item}\r\n{%endforeach}\r\n\r\nYou can also track the status of this order by visiting your Orders at {%replacements.orderUrl}.\r\n\r\nPlease note each item(s) may be shipped at different times. You can always log into your account to check the status of your items at {%replacements.orderUrl}.\r\n\r\nOriginal & Limited Edition works are carefully packaged, shipped, and handled directly by the artist. Shipping time frames vary based on which country the artist is shipping from (origin) and where it is being shipped to (destination).\r\n\r\nOpen Edition Prints, Canvases and Framed Prints are printed on demand and are shipped directly to you from our printers. We have printers located throughout the world.\r\n\r\nOriginal works of art can take up to 3 weeks to be received. Prints can take up to 2 weeks to be delivered.\r\n\r\nEach shipment is tracked by our shipping professionals.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions regarding this purchase, please contact us at {%replacements.replyEmail}, and we will assist you shortly.\r\n\r\nThank you for supporting our artists on Saatchi Online.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nSaatchi Online','<p>Dear {%replacements.profileName},</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">Saatchi Online would like to let you know that we&#39;ve shipped your artwork.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The following item has been shipped to you:<br />\r\n{%art_title}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TrackingUrls: {%foreach data=tracking_urls item=item}<br />\r\n{%item} {%endforeach}</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">You can also track the status of this order by visiting your Orders at {%replacements.orderUrl}.</s