  (18,'print_purchased','You just sold a print on Saatchi Online',NULL,'Dear {%profileName},\r\n\r\nCongratulations! You have just sold a print of {%artTitle}.  \r\n\r\nYour Payout will not be available until after artwork has been shipped and received by the collector (http://www.saatchionline.com/help#request-a-payout). \r\n\r\nPlease note that in order to start receiving payments from Saatchi Online, you must provide the appropriate signed tax forms which you can find at http://www.saatchionline.com/taxes/.\r\n\r\nSaatchi Online requires all artists to submit a signed tax form (W9 for US residents, W8-BEN for Non-US residents) prior to processing artist payouts.  Tax forms are not accepted without your signature. Non-US residents may also apply for an ITIN (Individual Txapayer Identification Number). Without an ITIN, we will be required to deduct a 30% US Witholding Tax.\r\n\r\nSubmit completed tax forms to us via email at support{%saatchionline}.com.\r\n\r\nThank you for being part of the Saatchi Online community.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nThe Saatchi Online Team','Dear {%profileName},<br/>\r\n<br/>\r\nCongratulations! You have just sold a print of {%artTitle}.<br/>  \r\n<br/>\r\nYour Payout will not be available until after artwork has been shipped and received by the collector <a href=\"http://www.saatchionline.com/help#request-a-payout\">(http://www.saatchionline.com/help#request-a-payout)</a>.<br/> \r\n<br/>\r\nPlease note that in order to start receiving payments from Saatchi Online, you must provide the appropriate signed tax forms which you can find at <a href=\"http://www.saatchionline.com/taxes/\">http://www.saatchionline.com/taxes/</a>.<br/>\r\n<br/>\r\nSaatchi Online requires all artists to submit a signed tax form (W9 for US residents, W8-BEN for Non-US residents) prior to processing artist payouts.  Tax forms are not accepted without your signature. Non-US residents may also apply for an ITIN (Individual Txapayer Identification Number). Without an ITIN, 